WEBVTT

00:00:00.619 --> 00:00:03.484
BAARBA, TZIPI KICHLER MERAYENET ET HUGO

00:00:03.484 --> 00:00:06.046
Hershi Tsvi Fishman.

00:00:07.268 --> 00:00:16.509
ven der S.S. treft mikh dort, hot er mikh zofort arop geshosn, on keyn shum tayne-umaynes, vayl s'iz geven aroysgegebn a gezets az dort tor men nisht zayn.

00:00:17.578 --> 00:00:19.901
hot men mir gezogt az der geshmak

00:00:20.093 --> 00:00:21.693
vos der UNK

00:00:21.693 --> 00:00:27.883
hot aroys gegebn hot dem hint nisht gelozt araynkumen dort tsu mir.

00:00:28.412 --> 00:00:30.830
azoy bin ikh matsl gevorn fun dort,

00:00:30.830 --> 00:00:34.493
un azoy vi ikh hob dos gezen, dos iz nisht keyn gesheft,

00:00:34.493 --> 00:00:36.610
mer bin ikh nisht gegangen ahin,

00:00:36.610 --> 00:00:38.430
un ikh hob mikh tsurik gemoldn

00:00:38.672 --> 00:00:41.383
ineveynik un ikh bin tsurik gegangen

00:00:41.490 --> 00:00:42.702
arbetn dort

00:00:42.702 --> 00:00:45.550
tsu der tsu dem plats.

00:00:46.705 --> 00:00:50.243
dort hot men gearbet vi azoy, s'shver geven,

00:00:50.248 --> 00:00:55.254
tseklopt finger, dos iz dokh nisht keyn groyse zakh shoyn haynt mit vos ven,

00:00:55.783 --> 00:00:58.105
vi lang bistu dort geven?

00:00:56.728 --> 00:00:59.962
yo, un dort ze'mir opgezesn

00:01:00.053 --> 00:01:05.261
biz in tsvelftn april toyznt nayn hundert finef un fertsik.

00:01:05.689 --> 00:01:13.069
dentsmol hobn shoyn ongehoybn tsu kumen noent der front der amerikaner armey dortemen,

00:01:13.069 --> 00:01:14.390
mit englisher,

00:01:14.413 --> 00:01:17.901
hot men dem gantsn lager oysgeleydikt,

00:01:18.042 --> 00:01:23.368
un ho'mir ongehoybn tsu geyn oyf di vegn, vi azoy m'zogt der marsh,

00:01:23.172 --> 00:01:24.263
toytn-marsh.

00:01:23.779 --> 00:01:25.210
toytn-marsh.

00:01:25.210 --> 00:01:26.422
ze'mir gegangen.

00:01:26.952 --> 00:01:39.039
un azoy ze'mir gegangen, gegangen tog un nakht, ongekumen, durkh gegangen azoyne shtet tsum bayshpil vi Tsvikau vayl dos zenen geven shtet bakante vey- gedenk ikh es, derflekh gedenk ikh nisht,

00:01:39.039 --> 00:01:41.705
ober undz hot men gefirt di zaytn

00:01:41.705 --> 00:01:43.382
vegn, nisht durkh di vegn.

00:01:43.692 --> 00:01:49.592
un azoy gedenk ikh azoy vi haynt, dort iz geven veldlekh, velder un vos ven, un dan oyf der nakht

00:01:50.273 --> 00:01:53.391
ver geyt a klang az der nakht

00:01:53.391 --> 00:01:57.759
geyt zayn tsores, m'shist oys. mentshn.

00:01:59.031 --> 00:02:02.653
un vos tut men?

00:02:03.334 --> 00:02:08.089
hot men tseshpreyt ale mentshn in aza vald, dort s'geven beymer,

00:02:08.089 --> 00:02:10.635
un s'iz geven aropgefalene tsaygn.

00:02:11.485 --> 00:02:17.959
hob ikh mikh badekt vi azoy m'zogt mit azoyne tsvaygn, vifl s'iz geven hob ikh oyf mir aroyfgeleygt.

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:20.186
un ven s'hot zikh gemakht tog

00:02:20.867 --> 00:02:25.771
kh'bin aroysgekukt tsu do, tsu dort un vos ven, s'nisht geven

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:27.881
gornisht, s'nisht gegangen.

00:02:28.461 --> 00:02:32.285
azoy ze'mir gegangen vayter, gegangen un gegangen,

00:02:32.443 --> 00:02:35.103
un ze'mir ongekumen, gegesn iz nisht geven.

00:02:35.498 --> 00:02:38.591
gegesn ho'mir gegesn vos ho'mir getrofn

00:02:38.591 --> 00:02:40.773
s'do azoyne vortslen

00:02:41.117 --> 00:02:43.946
vos s'vaksn oyf di velder

00:02:44.205 --> 00:02:45.096
mit a,

00:02:45.096 --> 00:02:48.530
dort iz geven der groyser daytsher

00:02:48.530 --> 00:02:51.644
boyern hobn dort riblekh a sakh un vos ven,

00:02:51.644 --> 00:02:55.711
s'in a roy rible, halb roy rible, hob ikh nokh getoygt oyfesn.

00:02:55.711 --> 00:03:01.209
mer hob ikh nisht getoygt, s'ongekumen tsu brekhn, un aza petrishke azoy vi m'zogt, yo.

00:03:01.688 --> 00:03:04.730
nu, un ze'mir ongekumen oyfn

00:03:04.730 --> 00:03:09.473
barg fun Erts, Erts-Gebit, azoy heyst der barg,

00:03:09.473 --> 00:03:11.624
vos er firt ariber fun Daytshland

00:03:11.624 --> 00:03:13.286
oyf Tshekhoslovakay.

00:03:13.286 --> 00:03:17.240
oyf Sudetn-Gebit, un Pilzen, dort oyf yene gegnter.

00:03:18.276 --> 00:03:23.605
dort hot undz in a tog gekhapt a regn oyf yenem,

00:03:23.605 --> 00:03:26.809
az m'hot nisht getoygt UNK. plutsem,

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:33.122
ze'mir geven dort, zog'mir ikh veys, a dray fir hundert mentshn, shoyn vayl dort iz shoyn geven tseteylt ver s'geyt oyf

00:03:33.122 --> 00:03:37.097
oyf mayrev, un ver s'geyt oyf mizrekh. Eyrope.

00:03:37.097 --> 00:03:38.604
dort hot men zikh tseteylt.

00:03:38.610 --> 00:03:41.236
undz ze'mir geblibn dort a dray fir hundert mentshn,

00:03:41.344 --> 00:03:45.897
un plutsem di dray fir hundert mentshn, vi vilde khayes,

00:03:45.897 --> 00:03:48.757
heybn on tsurik tsu loyfn, nisht oyf ur,

00:03:48.757 --> 00:03:50.690
nor tsurik. di S.S.n

00:03:50.690 --> 00:03:53.083
shteyen, un vos hot zikh pasirt?

00:03:53.089 --> 00:03:56.233
dort iz geven aza kabine,

00:03:56.233 --> 00:04:03.337
aza shayer, vu m'hot gehaltn shtroy, mit, di di poyern velkhe zey hobn dort gehat felder,

00:04:03.337 --> 00:04:07.190
un yeder hot zikh ahin araynge⟨UNK⟩ vegn regn.

00:04:07.787 --> 00:04:09.975
ikh bin mikh ongekumen bay der tir,

00:04:10.791 --> 00:04:16.944
un nishto keyn nodl ken men nisht aropredn, un ikh azoy vi ikh bin geven gevoynt mit azoy derferishe mayses,

00:04:17.153 --> 00:04:20.364
gib ikh a kuk, dort iz do aza grinder, vi m'zogt,

00:04:20.364 --> 00:04:23.030
dort iz fray, s'nokh do eyns, tsvey,

00:04:23.030 --> 00:04:25.669
ikh drape mikh aroyf

00:04:25.793 --> 00:04:26.920
oyf dem

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:29.803
azoy boydem, s'nisht geven keyn breter,

00:04:29.860 --> 00:04:33.330
un ikh zets mikh dort arop, un fun dort

00:04:33.353 --> 00:04:34.528
kuk ikh

00:04:35.108 --> 00:04:37.498
zeks un draysik sho,

00:04:37.892 --> 00:04:40.046
vos s'tut zikh untn.

00:04:40.187 --> 00:04:42.715
un untn, bay nakht,

00:04:42.715 --> 00:04:44.940
hobn zikh mentshn geshtokhn

00:04:45.064 --> 00:04:46.880
eyns dos andere

00:04:47.511 --> 00:04:56.820
ve- velkher iz gezi- gelign eyns lebn andern, hot gevolt yens plats, yener hot gevolt yens plats, iz er arayngekumen, im arop geshtokhn, aroysgevorfn.

00:04:57.417 --> 00:05:03.486
un azoy ze'mir dort gezesn, azoy iz dos durkhgegangen a por tog, khotsh a fir finef tog,

00:05:04.386 --> 00:05:08.227
hot men ongehoybn tsu brengen, ikh veys fun vu di S.S.n hobn dos ba-

00:05:08.723 --> 00:05:12.784
ge- tsugekumen, epes zup fun fun azoyne berekes,

00:05:12.790 --> 00:05:14.893
tsuker-berekes hot dos geheysn,

00:05:15.287 --> 00:05:19.533
un iz men aropgegangen nokh aza tsuker-berekes trinken.

00:05:19.911 --> 00:05:24.950
dervayl hot zikh dort tsamgenumen a kupe toyte mentshn vos zenen dort derharget gevorn,

00:05:25.058 --> 00:05:28.342
un mentshn velkhe zenen, zey hobn nokh gedekhet,

00:05:28.770 --> 00:05:30.569
s'nokh geven lebn in zey,

00:05:30.627 --> 00:05:33.230
velkhe zenen geshtanen dort hot men zey gekhapt,

00:05:33.230 --> 00:05:34.724
un aroysgevorfn

00:05:34.724 --> 00:05:36.746
tsam gevorfn, dort iz geven a grub.

00:05:38.102 --> 00:05:40.427
a klal, hobn di S.S.n gezogt, nu,

00:05:40.427 --> 00:05:44.221
kumts, khevre, nishto keyn mayses, di mentshn

00:05:44.768 --> 00:05:47.732
grobt ir, dos iz geven a lebn aza veldl,

00:05:48.058 --> 00:05:50.701
ze'mir genumen undz fir finef

00:05:50.826 --> 00:05:52.426
khevre layt, azoyne

00:05:52.426 --> 00:05:55.579
vi ikh, undzere khaveyrim ze'mir dort geven,

00:05:55.669 --> 00:05:58.565
un geshtelt dort grobn azoyne

00:05:58.572 --> 00:06:00.450
griber, vi ven,

00:06:00.450 --> 00:06:02.559
un fun dort ho'mir genumen

00:06:02.559 --> 00:06:06.559
di toyte un dort arayngevorfn.

00:06:06.559 --> 00:06:07.858
dort, dos haynt,

00:06:07.858 --> 00:06:10.836
az ikh zol geyn dortemen, derken ikh dos plats

00:06:10.836 --> 00:06:12.909
vu dos iz geven.

00:06:13.928 --> 00:06:15.576
vos iz geven vayter?

00:06:13.962 --> 00:06:17.764
nu, i- azoy ze'mir undz gegangen nokh dem vayter,

00:06:17.764 --> 00:06:27.573
undz ho'mir gebroykht arayngeyn keyn Tshekhoslovakay, vayl dort iz nokh geven fray der veg, dort iz nokh nisht geven keyn mil- nokh nisht geven keyn milkhome.

00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:31.306
ongekumen keyn Tshekhoslova- oyf yene zayt,

00:06:31.306 --> 00:06:35.508
ye- dort, yene S.S.n hobn undz nisht gelozt arayngeyn.

00:06:35.508 --> 00:06:37.144
hot nisht gelozt m'zol undz

00:06:37.144 --> 00:06:39.642
araynfirn ahin tsu di S.S.n.

00:06:39.642 --> 00:06:41.783
un m'hot undz tsurik getribn,

00:06:41.974 --> 00:06:47.050
azoy az shtots dem zol'mir geven dentsmol arayngeyn ahin, hot men undz tsurik getribn,

00:06:47.050 --> 00:06:48.954
un ze'mir ongekumen

00:06:48.977 --> 00:06:50.760
oyf a gegnt

00:06:50.985 --> 00:06:52.447
vos s'heyst,

00:06:53.652 --> 00:06:55.333
vayl dos derfl

00:06:55.457 --> 00:06:56.463
hob ikh

00:06:56.470 --> 00:06:58.365
shoyn nisht azoy der-

00:06:58.365 --> 00:07:01.206
dermant mikh zeyer shver,

00:07:01.347 --> 00:07:04.276
un s'hot geheysn Netnirsh.

00:07:04.485 --> 00:07:09.913
dos iz bay Tshekhn Tshekhn geven, oyf der grenets fun Sudetn-Gebit,

00:07:09.919 --> 00:07:11.415
lebn a barg,

00:07:11.995 --> 00:07:18.654
un ahin, nokh ikh veys vifl teg, ze'mir ongekumen dort, dort geven aza groyser

00:07:18.795 --> 00:07:34.891
oykhet shayer fun fun fun poyern, vos zey hobn dort gehat di felder, hobn dort gehat azoyne, vu zey hobn gehaltn di di beheymes, tsi, ober dentsmol iz es geven leydik vayl s'nisht geven. un dos iz geven bayleyfik hundert meter, zog'mir akhtsik meter, hundert meter, funem KVISH, funem hoypt

00:07:34.891 --> 00:07:39.006
KVISH, azoy arayn tsum in vald arayn, lebn vald.

00:07:39.467 --> 00:07:43.404
dort hot men undz gehaltn akht tog, tsi zibn tog,

00:07:43.404 --> 00:07:46.211
a- tsu fri ze'mir aroysgegangen,

00:07:46.251 --> 00:07:49.535
un nokh mitog tsurikgegangen.

00:07:49.693 --> 00:07:50.913
in a tog,

00:07:50.913 --> 00:07:52.356
zogn di S.S.n,

00:07:52.356 --> 00:07:55.458
ver s'shpirt zikh nisht gut, ver s'iz krank,

00:07:55.667 --> 00:08:00.195
ho'mir do tsvey vegn, aroyf oyf di vogn un mir firn'mir aykh

00:08:00.195 --> 00:08:04.506
ober keyn Bukhnvald, m'zol aykh a bisl unterhelfn,

00:08:04.506 --> 00:08:07.457
ober ikh veys vu in der nent.

00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:09.713
nu, ikh ho-

00:08:09.713 --> 00:08:14.848
ikh hob nisht gevolt azoy, ikh hob mikh geshpirt geyn gey ikh nokh, biz vi lang m'geyt geyt men.

00:08:15.006 --> 00:08:21.500
un zogt men dem farn kapo, s'geven zeyer mentsh, zeyer a guter bruder, un m'iz geven zeyer gut un vos ven,

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:29.034
zogt im, nu, du vest onfirn di ale kranke khevre layt. nu, m'zetst zey aroyf oyf di vegn un zey geyen, m'firt zey avek.

00:08:29.034 --> 00:08:30.102
avek avek.

00:08:30.885 --> 00:08:34.456
in a tog, undz gey'mir oyf azoy a veg,

00:08:34.631 --> 00:08:37.088
dortemen lebn aza ek shtroz,

00:08:37.720 --> 00:08:41.190
zogt eyner, kuk nor dort vos tut zikh. iz dort geven a kupe

00:08:43.508 --> 00:08:46.978
korbones, dort tsam gevorfn,

00:08:47.710 --> 00:08:51.166
un m'kukt azoy noent derkent men dem kapo oykhet.

00:08:51.166 --> 00:08:52.935
ale dort oysgeshosn.

00:08:52.992 --> 00:08:56.614
ale fun eynemen, der kapo vayl er iz geven zeyer guter bruder,

00:08:56.890 --> 00:09:01.018
un er iz geven a mentshn un, vi m'zogt, in ale koykhes.

00:09:01.125 --> 00:09:03.127
oykhet dort oysgeshosn.

00:09:05.209 --> 00:09:07.830
dort gehaltn vayter,

00:09:07.830 --> 00:09:15.193
un der front iz alts gekumen. in fiftn may, toyznt nayn hundert finef un fertsik oyf der nakht,

00:09:15.435 --> 00:09:20.781
ven undz ze'mir shoyn geven ineveynik in der shure, kumen di S.S.n un m'shrayt,

00:09:20.781 --> 00:09:24.896
"antretn! antretn!" m'zol ale aroyskumen.

00:09:25.138 --> 00:09:31.117
keyn mol hot men undz nisht aroysgenumen oyf der nakht, er hot getrogn bay tog, ven s'nokh geven tog, bay nakht hot men nisht genumen, vos ken dos tun?

00:09:31.117 --> 00:09:33.739
nu, m'shtelt undz di reye, ales UNK,

00:09:33.778 --> 00:09:37.336
der komendant dun di S.S.n ruft zey tsam,

00:09:37.336 --> 00:09:42.727
un m'zogt dort, epes vos ven, vos undz hobn nisht gehert, vos ven, nu, un m'rirt.

00:09:42.727 --> 00:09:46.107
fornt S.S.n, in di zaytn S.S.n, a hinter S.S.n,

00:09:46.198 --> 00:09:51.342
un undz shtots m'zol undz firn tsum KVISH, vayl hobn gerekhnt tsu geyn ergets,

00:09:51.342 --> 00:09:53.533
hot men undz arayngefirt in vald.

00:09:53.623 --> 00:09:56.858
nu, hobn mir gezogt, do iz shoyn frish.

00:09:57.150 --> 00:09:58.978
oys, kaputers,

00:09:58.978 --> 00:10:05.278
shoyn finftn, di di di di di shiserayen hot zikh shoyn gehert, di UNK, di AVYONen, fun iberol

00:10:07.326 --> 00:10:11.674
un ze'mir gegangen a tsvey dray sho, ze'mir ongekumen oyf aza shpits barg,

00:10:11.983 --> 00:10:13.766
nemt undz der S.S.,

00:10:14.633 --> 00:10:15.673
shtil blaybn.

00:10:15.966 --> 00:10:17.445
zogt er, herts oys,

00:10:17.637 --> 00:10:20.567
in Tshekhoslovakay iz a revolutsye.

00:10:21.079 --> 00:10:22.203
di tshekhn

00:10:22.665 --> 00:10:27.893
kemfn kegn di daytshn. dos iz geven in fiftn zekstn may, dentsl hobn di tshekhn nokh,

00:10:27.893 --> 00:10:32.750
s'shoyn geven bald ende di krig, ober di tshekhn hobn gekemft, gemakht a revolutsye.

00:10:32.976 --> 00:10:33.932
zogt er,

00:10:33.955 --> 00:10:36.784
undz lo'mir ets aykh do, zogt er,

00:10:37.043 --> 00:10:43.162
ir zolt oyfpasn vu ir geyt, zogt er, vayl ir vet aykh trefn mit andere S.S.n. yener makht,

00:10:44.147 --> 00:10:46.723
un di hobn undz dort gelozt in mitn feld.

00:10:46.898 --> 00:10:48.090
nu!

00:10:47.151 --> 00:10:49.305
dos iz geven der bafrayung?

00:10:48.197 --> 00:10:50.401
dos iz geven undzer bafrayung.

00:10:50.813 --> 00:10:52.190
nu, vos tut men?

00:10:53.007 --> 00:10:55.093
ho'mir zikh koydem aropgezetst.

00:10:55.116 --> 00:10:56.173
a bisl zikh

00:10:56.365 --> 00:10:59.171
oyszen tsi s'iz emes, tsi nisht emes.

00:10:59.171 --> 00:11:01.736
un ho'mir zikh dort azoy aropgeleygt unter a boym,

00:11:01.736 --> 00:11:02.993
heyst unter a

00:11:02.993 --> 00:11:06.348
a b- a a ployt,

00:11:06.625 --> 00:11:07.887
zol men zikh nisht

00:11:07.887 --> 00:11:14.111
emetser trefn, vos ven, un mir gey'mir, s'hot zikh azoy genumen tog ma- makhn, un mir gey'mir vayter.

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:19.376
s'hot zikh gemakht tog, iz geven dort khevre vos hobn gekent gut daytsh, un vos ven,

00:11:20.057 --> 00:11:22.248
hot men zey geshikt, nu, gey ze

00:11:22.248 --> 00:11:26.076
a dorf shoyn, mentshn, vu mir ze'mir, vos ven.

00:11:26.470 --> 00:11:31.391
nu, kumen zey tsurik, oy! zogt er, undz ze'mir in dem dorf,

00:11:31.785 --> 00:11:33.163
vos ikh hob frier gezogt,

00:11:33.237 --> 00:11:39.626
vu ze'mir geven nekhtn nakht, dem gantsn veg vos undz ze'mir gegangen ho'mir zikh gedreyt azoy ibern dort

00:11:39.632 --> 00:11:45.819
un nekhtn nakht zenen do arayngekumen di amerikaner, der amerikaner armey.

00:11:45.910 --> 00:12:02.258
ven di S.S.n hobn undz aroysgefirt in vald, iz oyfn KVISH durkh geforn der amerikaner armey, ober zey zenen nisht gegangen iberol kukn, dort iz a geboy muz men geyn zen vos ven, dort iz a geboy iz a geboy, vos ven, zey gegangen vayter.

00:12:02.258 --> 00:12:06.035
di S.S.n hobn ober shoyn gevust di mayse,

00:12:06.109 --> 00:12:07.925
hobn undz farfirt,

00:12:08.387 --> 00:12:12.020
un undz gelozt, zey zenen zikher ongetun

00:12:12.020 --> 00:12:16.079
pr- tsivile kleydung zikher gehat ergets tsugegreyt,

00:12:16.079 --> 00:12:20.041
un undz dort gelozt. nu, undz ze'mir arayngegangen dortn in dorf,

00:12:20.115 --> 00:12:22.387
un zikh dortn getrofn mit di

00:12:22.410 --> 00:12:24.735
mit di amerikaner armey.

