nu yene amerikaner hobn mir, punkt mit undz hobn zey gehat tsu tun, yene, zey hobn gezen mentshn geyn, geyn, zey hobn shoyn gezen azoyne heftlingen, zenen nisht geven di

00:12:33.595 --> 00:12:36.140
ershte, ze'mir shoyn geven ikh veys vifldike,

00:12:35.910 --> 00:12:37.861
ikh vil dikh fregn,

