dos iz geven,

00:12:38.205 --> 00:12:41.996
bist tsurikgekumen tsurikgekumen keyn Siget?

00:12:41.698 --> 00:12:42.519
yo.

00:12:42.593 --> 00:12:44.308
vos hostu dort getrofn?

00:12:45.006 --> 00:12:47.902
in Siget hob ikh nisht getrofn gornisht.

00:12:47.942 --> 00:12:54.905
dos iz azoy vi azoy dos lidl zogt men, "vu hin zol ikh geyn?" iz do aza lidl fun UNK.

00:12:55.350 --> 00:13:05.334
ober fun ven ikh bin arayn keyn Siget, iz do do der gantser veg iz geven ales interesant, nor eyn zakh vil ikh nokh, vayl se s'karakterizirt der mayse.

00:13:05.695 --> 00:13:08.456
oyfn veg vi azoy ze'mir gekumen fun

00:13:08.513 --> 00:13:11.986
fun fun Tshekhoslovakay,

00:13:11.986 --> 00:13:13.538
tsu fus, mitn

00:13:13.538 --> 00:13:16.944
mitn tsug, vos m'hot getrofn, vos ven, biz keyn

00:13:17.068 --> 00:13:18.255
biz keyn Siget,

00:13:18.255 --> 00:13:20.741
far Siget ze'mir ongekumen, dos iz do

00:13:20.848 --> 00:13:26.717
Slotvine heyst es, dos iz a shtet- a derfl, a shtetl, oyf der tshekhisher zayt.

00:13:26.717 --> 00:13:30.312
az m'zol aribergeyn keyn Siget, broykht men durkhgeyn a groys vaser,

00:13:30.312 --> 00:13:32.351
dos heyst der Tas, der Tisa.

00:13:32.357 --> 00:13:39.219
broykh men durkhgeyn dentsmol der brik hot der milkhome tseshmetert, hot men gebroykht durkhgeyn mit azoyne

00:13:39.732 --> 00:13:42.358
shif- vos shiflekh, mit azoyne

00:13:42.567 --> 00:13:45.036
vi azoy, ikh veys vi azoy m'zogt dos,

00:13:44.558 --> 00:13:45.682
RAFSOD.

00:13:46.077 --> 00:13:50.644
mit a, mit vos m'tut halt- mit di hent geyn, nu.

00:13:51.038 --> 00:13:52.922
SCSONAKn, azoy hot dos geheysn.

00:13:53.367 --> 00:13:58.035
nu, un dort oyf der nakht, ze'mir ongekumen oyf der nakht in dem

00:13:58.075 --> 00:14:00.535
in dem derfl Slatvina, yo,

00:14:00.535 --> 00:14:02.037
un ho'mir gezogt, nu,

00:14:02.037 --> 00:14:08.717
s'do a leydike shtub dort, vayl di geven yidishe shtiber leydik mit vos ven, ho'mir zikh dort aropgeleygt, zo'mir durkh shlofn di nakht.

00:14:09.229 --> 00:14:13.537
tsu fri, mir gey mir, un i- ikh bin a bisl arop geblibn, undz geyn UNK.

00:14:13.537 --> 00:14:19.280
ikh plutsem her ikh a veyn, a geshrey, oy! vos hot zikh, ikh kum on ahin, vos hot zikh pasirt?

00:14:19.658 --> 00:14:22.115
a meydl fun Borsho

00:14:22.408 --> 00:14:25.155
hot zikh geshlept fun Daytshland,

00:14:25.155 --> 00:14:27.043
dos heyst, ikh veys vifl

00:14:27.505 --> 00:14:30.233
hunderter tsi toyznt kilometer,

00:14:30.576 --> 00:14:34.130
mit a skhoyre, mit a layvnt, Damask,

00:14:34.457 --> 00:14:37.795
dos iz a, di beste layvnt skhoyre.

00:14:37.795 --> 00:14:40.951
un zi hot dos gevolt fun Daytshland

00:14:40.951 --> 00:14:42.638
onbrengen biz keyn

00:14:42.638 --> 00:14:44.711
Borsho, hot zi dos geshlept

00:14:44.717 --> 00:14:46.815
toyznt kilometer, tsi vifl,

00:14:46.815 --> 00:14:49.009
un zi iz ongekumen dort tsum vaser,

00:14:49.009 --> 00:14:51.447
zenen ongekumen rusisher soldatn,

00:14:51.447 --> 00:14:54.350
un m'hot dos fun ir tsugenumen,

00:14:54.350 --> 00:15:02.632
un di zenen zikh avek, un dos meydl iz geblibn on gornisht, zi hot zikh geshlept a monat hot zi zikh geshlept mit dem azoy fil veg, nu.

00:15:02.803 --> 00:15:05.349
vos iz geven mit dir? vos hostu getun?

00:15:04.883 --> 00:15:07.492
bin ikh aribergegangen in Siget,

00:15:08.562 --> 00:15:20.418
koydem vu hin tsu geyn hob ikh nisht gehat, shoyn geven, ikh bin shoyn gegangen dort in ershtn tog, tsveytn tog, dort vu undz ho'mir gevoynt, vayl ikh hob gevust dort tref ikh dokh nisht gornisht, un vos ven,

00:15:21.167 --> 00:15:29.919
bin ikh arayn iz dort geven a shnayderay, a kooperative vi m'iz tsurikgekumen fun der krig, oykh geven yinglekh vi ikh, shnayders, un oykh nisht gehat,

00:15:29.031 --> 00:15:30.864
un dort hostu gearbet?

00:15:30.027 --> 00:15:34.172
yo, bin ikh arayn dort ahin, dort hob ikh gearbet in ershte tsaytn,

00:15:35.578 --> 00:15:38.275
un dort hob ikh gearbet biz

00:15:38.275 --> 00:15:39.752
zeks un

00:15:39.752 --> 00:15:43.675
fertsik, ende zeks un f- fun finef un fer- ikh bin ongekumen in yuni

00:15:43.675 --> 00:15:45.236
finef un fertsik,

00:15:45.236 --> 00:15:47.404
hob ikh dort gearbet biz in

00:15:47.404 --> 00:15:49.072
oktober tsi ven,

00:15:49.180 --> 00:15:50.254
in Siget.

00:15:49.446 --> 00:15:51.890
ven hostu getrofn dayn froy?

00:15:51.711 --> 00:15:52.380
yo.

00:15:52.977 --> 00:15:57.698
in yene tsaytn azoy vi ikh gey eyn mol oyf der gas,

00:15:57.698 --> 00:16:05.981
un ikh hob zi gekent shoyn fun befor, als meydl, nisht UNK zi iz geven fun an andern dorf, hob ikh zi gekent, azoy iz geven,

00:16:06.460 --> 00:16:09.477
un ikh gey azoy oyf der gas, plutsem zi

00:16:09.477 --> 00:16:13.383
kumt mir akegn, zi iz dentsmol gekumen

00:16:13.383 --> 00:16:17.560
fun Oyshvits, zi iz dentsmol bafrayt gevorn dos, nisht bafrayt gevorn, nor

00:16:17.560 --> 00:16:19.768
zi iz geven in di rusishe

00:16:19.825 --> 00:16:27.075
lagers nokh, nokhn ba- nokh Oyshvits bafrayen, un zi iz shpeter ongekumen, zi iz ongekumen ersht ende oygust,

00:16:27.132 --> 00:16:29.693
onfang september, iz zi ongekumen keyn Siget.

00:16:29.693 --> 00:16:31.867
ikh gey oyf der gas un ikh tref mikh mit ir.

00:16:32.093 --> 00:16:34.652
nu, vos hob ikh getun? bin ikh gegangen ⟨hin aher⟩,

00:16:35.417 --> 00:16:38.232
vi azoy m'zogt, iz zi zi iz nisht geven keyn mies meydl un

00:16:38.232 --> 00:16:39.832
geven a sheyn meydl,

00:16:39.980 --> 00:16:50.143
un, ikh hob nisht oykh nisht gehat keynem, un zi hot oykh nisht gehat keynem, UNK zi hot gehat nor a feter in ergets un a mume in ergets, epes a dorf, vayt fun Siget.

00:16:50.318 --> 00:16:52.894
tsu ge- voynen iz nisht geven vu,

00:16:53.271 --> 00:16:57.585
haynt hot men geshlofn do, morgn hot men geshlofn dort bayn a khaver, dort a khaver,

00:16:57.810 --> 00:17:00.178
iz geven undzer a guter bruder,

00:17:00.178 --> 00:17:05.485
vos er hot geha- er iz nisht geven khasene, er iz geven elter fun undz, ober zayn familye iz oykh nisht tsurikgekumen

00:17:05.485 --> 00:17:07.777
er hot farshaft a groyse voynung,

00:17:07.800 --> 00:17:11.354
hot er gezogt, du, Hershl, kum tsun kum tsu mir!

00:17:11.682 --> 00:17:16.130
un zenen oykh gekumen andere, nokh tsvey aza

00:17:16.440 --> 00:17:18.644
yingl un meydl zenen gekumen,

00:17:18.718 --> 00:17:20.656
un ze'mir gekumen, ho'mir dort

00:17:20.656 --> 00:17:22.442
gevoynt in di ershte tsaytn,

00:17:22.228 --> 00:17:24.635
vi vi lang bistu dort gevoynt?

00:17:22.599 --> 00:17:23.285
iz

00:17:24.473 --> 00:17:26.812
dort hob ikh gevoynt

00:17:27.088 --> 00:17:30.139
ikh veys, a khotsh a yor, tsi vifl ven.

00:17:30.139 --> 00:17:34.949
un zi hot gehat a feter un a mume in a dorf, hobn zey gezogt, nu,

00:17:34.949 --> 00:17:37.765
az ir geyt shoyn azoy fil tsayt, m'vet makhn a khasene.

00:17:37.855 --> 00:17:42.610
un m'hot dort gemakht a khupe. dos zenen geven, vi azoy m'zogt, Hershl

00:17:42.610 --> 00:17:45.696
er iz gekumen in UNK, tsi er hot gevoynt in Bney Brak,

00:17:45.921 --> 00:17:47.554
geven a,

00:17:47.554 --> 00:17:52.243
i- a frumer yid, nisht ikh veys vos a min frumer, ober a yid UNK.

00:17:50.646 --> 00:17:53.711
un er hot gemakht di khupe?

00:17:52.637 --> 00:18:02.284
vi azoy, yo, dort hot men gemakht di khupe, di di mume, dos iz geven in november toyznt nayn hundert zeks un fertsik.

00:18:02.290 --> 00:18:03.482
iz dos geven.

00:18:02.644 --> 00:18:06.097
un dort hostu gevoynt nokh a por yor?

00:18:05.631 --> 00:18:07.737
ney- dos iz geven oyf a dorf.

00:18:07.737 --> 00:18:09.877
ober undz ze'mir tsurikgekumen keyn Siget.

00:18:09.968 --> 00:18:11.818
dort ho'mir gevoynt in Siget,

00:18:11.352 --> 00:18:14.704
un dort hostu gehat tsvey zin, yo, geboyrn?

00:18:13.191 --> 00:18:15.896
yo, dort iz zi, ney- eyner

00:18:15.896 --> 00:18:19.986
iz geboyrn gevorn in dort, dos heyst, nisht dort, in an andere shtot,

00:18:20.481 --> 00:18:31.309
un in in in der tsayt bin ikh aribergegangen, ibergelozt di shnayderay, un aribergegangen arbetn tsun an andere, tsun azoy vi m'zogt a tvue-gezelshaft.

00:18:31.315 --> 00:18:34.222
s'geven baym der medine, dos iz geven der shtat,

00:18:34.222 --> 00:18:42.986
bin ikh dort aribergegangen, ikh hob dos azoy vi m'zogt dos nisht farshtanen, s'geven azoy vi m'zogt a a hitl oyf a groysn, a groys hitl oyf a kleynem kop,

00:18:43.161 --> 00:18:46.952
nu, ober m'hot gezogt, dos iz, gey ahin, dos iz gut tsu arbetn,

00:18:46.519 --> 00:18:48.110
host gehat

00:18:48.110 --> 00:18:49.736
tsvey kinder, yo?

00:18:49.422 --> 00:18:50.260
yo.

00:18:49.877 --> 00:18:52.183
ven bistu gekumen keyn Erets Yisroel?

00:18:53.691 --> 00:18:56.244
ikh bin gekumen in

00:18:56.244 --> 00:19:00.536
khoydesh detsember, toyznt nayn hundert akht un akhtsik.

00:19:00.930 --> 00:19:04.197
biz akht un akhtsik bistu geven in Rumenye.

00:19:03.293 --> 00:19:05.109
bin ikh geven in Rumenye, yo.

00:19:05.567 --> 00:19:07.860
di kinder zenen geven kleyn,

00:19:07.866 --> 00:19:09.980
shpeter greser,

00:19:09.980 --> 00:19:12.871
host zey fartseylt vos host ibergelebt?

00:19:13.182 --> 00:19:14.661
nisht zeyer.

00:19:14.953 --> 00:19:18.508
alts epizodn, vi azoy m'zogt.

00:19:17.721 --> 00:19:20.786
un di froy hot oykh gornisht nisht dertseylt?

00:19:19.594 --> 00:19:20.763
oykh nisht.

00:19:20.763 --> 00:19:25.927
s'iz geven aza atmosfere di gantse tsaytn az s'nisht gekumen

00:19:25.927 --> 00:19:29.344
tsu redn iber azoyne problemen.

00:19:29.344 --> 00:19:32.328
shpeter ven zey zenen shoyn a bisl greser gevorn,

00:19:32.402 --> 00:19:37.554
ho'mir ongehoybn tsu dertseyln iber dem, iber yenem, ober azoy a gantse mayse,

00:19:37.554 --> 00:19:39.939
arop tsu tseyln, vos ven, dos iz nisht

00:19:40.013 --> 00:19:42.454
dos iz nisht geven di gantse tsayt.

00:19:42.544 --> 00:19:46.976
un far vos azoy lang bistu dort gevoynt un nisht gekumen friert keyn Yisroel?

00:19:46.847 --> 00:19:52.345
der groyser zun iz shoyn gekumen in toyznt nayn hundert akht un zibetsik. aher.

00:19:52.345 --> 00:19:57.709
der klenerer iz ge- ongekumen toyznt nayn hundert fir un akhtsik. far vos ze'men undz gekumen azoy shpet?

00:19:58.052 --> 00:20:00.436
di kinder hobn gevaksn,

00:20:00.436 --> 00:20:04.306
gelernt hobn zey gut un zenen arayn in di groyse shuln.

00:20:04.363 --> 00:20:05.791
der groyser.

00:20:06.321 --> 00:20:08.950
un biz vi lang er hot nisht gemakht

00:20:08.950 --> 00:20:11.343
fartik gemakht di groyse shuln,

00:20:11.518 --> 00:20:14.110
hot zikh gemakht toyznt nayn hundert

00:20:14.269 --> 00:20:18.380
akht un z- koydem zog mir fir finef un zibetsik iz er fartik gevorn,

00:20:18.420 --> 00:20:25.968
un er iz arayn als ⟨mandirsk⟩ in a fabrik dort hot er gearbet, vi azoy m'makht papirn, un m'makht UNK, hot zikh gemakht akht un zibetsik.

00:20:25.968 --> 00:20:29.264
in der tsayt hot zikh der gr- kleyner oykhet

00:20:29.457 --> 00:20:31.462
oy- oyfgehoybn,

00:20:31.462 --> 00:20:40.532
un er iz oykhet arayn in a shul in Bukarest, Bukarest hobn zey gelernt ale tsvey, nisht in a gr- groyse, not eynfakh in aza tekhnike shul,

00:20:40.532 --> 00:20:42.540
er iz oykhet arayn ahin,

00:20:42.540 --> 00:20:44.841
un m'iz oykhet aheymgekumen un

00:20:45.252 --> 00:20:47.721
biz lang s'hot zikh gedreyt hot zikh azoy,

00:20:47.648 --> 00:20:54.071
yetst yetst voynen ale do in Yisroel, yo? tsvey zin un vifl eyniklekh?

00:20:47.721 --> 00:20:48.874
UNK

00:20:49.673 --> 00:20:51.590
yo, yetst voynen ale do.

00:20:52.812 --> 00:20:54.358
fir eyniklekh.

00:20:54.820 --> 00:20:58.003
dray yinglekh un eyn meydele.

00:20:58.414 --> 00:20:59.133
yo.

00:20:59.359 --> 00:21:05.057
vos vilstu oyfn sof fun di KALETET, vos vilstu zogn tsu di eyniklekh?

00:21:06.497 --> 00:21:10.811
di eyniklekh, vi azoy ikh ze, geyen zey oyf a gutn veg.

00:21:11.340 --> 00:21:13.952
ober du, vos vilstu zogn zey?

00:21:13.905 --> 00:21:15.738
vos ikh vil zogn zey.

00:21:16.082 --> 00:21:23.892
az koydem zoln visn der goyrl vos hot dos yidntum hot durkh gelebt,

00:21:23.892 --> 00:21:28.007
fun yener gegnt, fun Eyrope, fun vu undz kum'mir.

00:21:29.042 --> 00:21:38.548
un az dos eyntslne veg vi azoy m'zogt oyf take ruik tsu lebn, als, ikh meyn ruik tsu lebn, vi azoy m'lebt do, ober ikh meyn als yid,

00:21:38.548 --> 00:21:41.999
tsu lebn tsvishn mentshn un zikh shpirn als mentsh,

00:21:41.999 --> 00:21:43.110
iz do.

00:21:43.318 --> 00:21:45.792
vayl say vi zey ebn geyn,

00:21:46.002 --> 00:21:49.455
vet er hayntike velt als zayn

00:21:49.967 --> 00:21:54.866
dos, du bist yens un du bist dos, vayl dos antviklt zikh haynt

00:21:54.866 --> 00:22:04.426
nokh shtarker, azoy vi undz ze'mir iberol. broykhstu zen der iz a daytsh, der iz a rumener, un der iz a dos, un yeder kukt oyfn andern

00:22:04.426 --> 00:22:11.496
mit shlekhte oygn, azoy az do iz dos plats vu zey zenen, un vi azoy ikh ze,

00:22:11.496 --> 00:22:14.868
hobn zey take in do dos plats, zey lernen gut,

00:22:15.010 --> 00:22:17.791
zey lernen di toyre, vi azoy m'zogt,

00:22:17.791 --> 00:22:21.973
der gr- der groyser, ikh hob do a groys eynikl do in Tel-Aviv,

00:22:22.047 --> 00:22:27.925
ven er hot ongehoybn tsu lernen zogt er, nu, zog mir nor, vi azoy iz geven mit Av- Avrohom Avinu?

00:22:27.925 --> 00:22:29.696
yo, azoy hot er mir ongehoybn, zogt er.

00:22:29.696 --> 00:22:31.485
ober mit Moyshen,

00:22:31.485 --> 00:22:33.240
mit Moyshen, vos ven,

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:33.864
nu,

00:22:33.864 --> 00:22:39.641
azoyne kleynikeytn, nisht ales veys ikh im vi azoy m'ri- vi azoy m'lernt do,

00:22:40.137 --> 00:22:47.854
un un undz hof'mir az zey, di kinder ze ikh hobn zikh do ayngelebt,

00:22:47.854 --> 00:22:52.686
der groyser arbet bay di KHEVRA KHESHMAL un er iz tsufridn, vi azoy m'zogt,

00:22:52.692 --> 00:22:55.622
der kleyner bay di TADIRAN,

00:22:55.847 --> 00:23:01.966
er iz oykh tsufridn, vi azoy m'zogt, se vi azoy m'zogt, s'ken zayn beser ober beser iz dokh nisht do keyn ende,

00:23:02.007 --> 00:23:04.357
un hofntlekh az

00:23:04.357 --> 00:23:05.729
zey ebn hobn

00:23:05.905 --> 00:23:10.219
a beser lebn vi undz ho'mir gehat dort.

00:23:10.309 --> 00:23:11.096
yo.

00:23:11.119 --> 00:23:12.356
zay gezunt.

00:23:12.317 --> 00:23:15.196
TODAH RABAH, TODAH RABAH, GAM ANI.

00:23:12.356 --> 00:23:13.208
TODAH RABAH.

00:23:18.949 --> 00:23:21.727
dos iz mayn vayb,

00:23:21.784 --> 00:23:24.343
vi m'zogt, zi heyst Khnatsl,

00:23:24.973 --> 00:23:29.050
fun di ir familye's zayt iz zi a rov's a eynikl.

00:23:29.091 --> 00:23:33.050
ir a- zeyde iz geven a rov in Rezavye,

00:23:33.445 --> 00:23:35.525
un zi heyst Kiselnik

00:23:35.525 --> 00:23:36.796
fun Borshe.

00:23:36.988 --> 00:23:39.513
heysn heyst zi Kiselnik Khantse,

00:23:39.604 --> 00:23:46.280
un ikh hob mikh mit ir bakont gemakht in toyznt nayn hundert eynem un fertsik hob ikh zi shoyn gekent,

00:23:46.438 --> 00:23:52.949
ober ikh bin nisht geven vi azoy m'zogt az zi vet zayn mayn vayb. der goyrl hot azoy gebrengt

00:23:52.949 --> 00:23:57.134
az in toyznt nayn hundert zeks un fertsik ho'mir zikh tsamgetrofn,

00:23:57.134 --> 00:24:02.024
un zayt dentsmol ze'mir in eynem, dos heyst shoyn iber fuftsik yor.

00:24:02.132 --> 00:24:06.513
ze'mir gekumen in land in toyznt nayn hundert akht un akhtsik, mir lebn mir do,

00:24:06.739 --> 00:24:09.382
undz ze'mir, vi azoy m'zogt, BARUCH HASHEM

00:24:09.439 --> 00:24:16.287
gut, mir shpir'mir zikh, zi hot a bisl hitster ongehoybn zikh nisht gut tsu shpirn, hofntlekh s'vet gut zayn,

00:24:16.287 --> 00:24:21.881
un azoy vet es zayn hofntlekh biz hundert un tsvontsik yor, mir zol'mir hobn nakhes fun di eyniklekh,

00:24:21.881 --> 00:24:25.433
un zol'mir zey zen zey antviklte

00:24:25.433 --> 00:24:27.675
mentshn do in land.

00:24:30.347 --> 00:24:36.199
oyf der oyfnamung iz mayn shvester iz di mitlste, Leye heyst zi,

00:24:36.199 --> 00:24:39.065
un ir man heyst Nandor, mitn kind.

00:24:39.190 --> 00:24:46.215
i zi i dos kind zenen avekgefirt gevorn keyn Oyshvits un dort farbrent gevorn, zenen nisht tsurikgekumen

00:24:46.215 --> 00:24:48.616
mer, mit di gantse familye.

00:24:51.745 --> 00:24:54.855
dos iz mayn shvester ven zi iz geven yinger,

00:24:54.855 --> 00:24:56.329
far der khasene,

00:24:56.622 --> 00:24:59.264
di iz Leye. vi azoy m'zogt.

00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:06.976
dos iz mayn klenste shvester, zi hot geheysn Sori.

00:25:07.050 --> 00:25:14.570
in toyznt nayn hundert fir un fertsik, ven m'hot zey deportirt keyn Oyshvits, iz zi alt geven dray un tsvontsik yor.

00:25:14.914 --> 00:25:19.802
zi iz farbrent gevorn in Oyshvits un nisht tsurikgekumen, mit di mame in eynem.

00:25:22.069 --> 00:25:28.441
dos bild iz gemakht gevorn in lager Goroyn, in toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un fertsik,

00:25:28.532 --> 00:25:37.756
ikh bin oyf der link zayt, vi azoy ikh shtey azoy antkegn, lebn shoymer, lebn dem zhandarm, azoy hot men zey gerufn.

00:25:38.269 --> 00:25:43.680
un di bilder mit nokh tsvey dray hob ikh bakumen in

00:25:43.686 --> 00:25:47.412
fun Budapest iz geven undzer a khaverte in Pest,

00:25:47.412 --> 00:25:50.076
un dort hot zi getrofn in muzeum,

00:25:50.098 --> 00:25:53.619
in muzeum fun Ungarn, un zi hot mir gebrengt di bilder.

00:25:56.865 --> 00:25:59.891
dos vos mir ze'mir iz undzer familye,

00:25:59.891 --> 00:26:04.571
lebn mir shteyt der groyser zun velkher er heyst Ilya,

00:26:04.797 --> 00:26:08.286
nokh im iz der klenerer zun vos er heyst Nikolay,

00:26:08.286 --> 00:26:10.764
un lebn zey di muter Khantsl.

00:26:12.441 --> 00:26:17.998
dos iz geven bayleyfik in toyznt nayn hundert,

00:26:17.998 --> 00:26:19.404
toyznt nayn hundert

00:26:20.929 --> 00:26:25.816
