00:27:05.636 --> 00:27:13.550
un ze- er arbet bay der TADIRAN, un zi arbet bayn a fabrik in Tel-Aviv vu m'makht tashkes.

00:27:13.550 --> 00:27:14.720
far froyen.

00:27:16.853 --> 00:27:18.382
di zenen mayne

00:27:18.912 --> 00:27:21.673
eyniklekh, baym klenern zun,

00:27:21.797 --> 00:27:25.228
